SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS "FrameSize", Sb.FpsLoad AS "FPS", Sb.PercentageLoad AS "Load", Sb.MbpsLoad AS "MbpsLoad", RxRes.DroppedFrameCount AS "DroppedCount", RxRes.ReorderedFrameCount AS "ReorderedCount", RxRes.DuplicateFrameCount AS "DuplicateCount", (SELECT Port.Location FROM Port WHERE Port.Handle = TxRes.ParentHnd) AS "TxPort", (SELECT Port.Location FROM Port WHERE Port.Handle = RxRes.ParentHnd) AS "RxPort" From RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock  = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle WHERE RxRes.IsExpectedPort=1

report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: Traffic received on all expected ports.
report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: Traffic not received on one or more expected ports.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT (CASE WHEN COUNT(*) > 0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) AS Verdict FROM RxExpectedTraffic

sql_statement.static: SELECT (SELECT CASE WHEN RxEotStreamResults.PortName IS NULL THEN RxEotStreamBlockResults.PortName ELSE RxEotStreamResults.PortName END) AS "Rx Port", (SELECT CASE WHEN RxEotStreamResults.FrameCount IS NULL THEN 'Port did not receive expected traffic.' ELSE 'Traffic received on unexpected port.' END) AS "Failure Reason" FROM RxEotStreamBlockResults LEFT OUTER JOIN RxEotStreamResults ON RxEotStreamBlockResults.ParentStreamBlock=RxEotStreamResults.ParentStreamBlock AND RxEotStreamBlockResults.ParentHnd=RxEotStreamResults.ParentHnd WHERE (RxEotStreamResults.FrameCount IS NULL) OR (RxEotStreamResults.IsExpectedPort=0)

report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: Tx frame count equals Rx frame count.
report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: Tx frame count doesn't equal Rx frame count.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT (CASE WHEN COUNT(*) > 0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) AS Verdict FROM IterationResults

sql_statement.static: SELECT RxPort AS "Rx Port", tx.FrameCount AS "Tx Frame Count", rx.FrameCount AS "Rx Frame Count", DroppedFrameCount AS "Dropped Frame Count", ReorderedFrameCount AS "Reordered Frame Count", DuplicateFrameCount AS "Duplicate Frame Count" FROM txeotstreamresults AS tx INNER JOIN rxeotstreamresults AS rx ON tx.StreamId=rx.Comp32 WHERE tx.FrameCount != (rx.FrameCount - rx.DuplicateFrameCount)

Properties.Name: SqlCreateTable
Properties.Value: CREATE TABLE MethRfc2544ThroughputFrameRate ('FrameSize' INTEGER, 'FPS' FLOAT, 'Load' FLOAT, 'DroppedCount' INTEGER, 'MaxRate' FLOAT, 'MaxLoad' FLOAT, 'RxLoad' FLOAT, 'RxFPS' FLOAT, 'LineSpeed' FLOAT, 'Converged' TEXT)

Properties.Name: SqlQuery
Properties.Value: SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', CASE WHEN Sb.FpsLoad < 0 THEN 0.00 ELSE ROUND(Sb.FpsLoad-0.005,2) END AS 'Frames per Second', Sb.PercentageLoad AS 'Load (%)', RxRes.DroppedFrameCount AS 'Dropped Frame Count', (Sb.FpsLoad * 100.0) / Sb.PercentageLoad AS 'Theoretical Max Rate', 100 'Max Load %', (CASE WHEN RxRes.IsExpectedPort=1 THEN ((((RxRes.L1BitCount / 1000000.0) / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) / ((Sb.MbpsLoad * 100.0) / Sb.PercentageLoad)) * 100.0) ELSE 0 END) AS 'Rx Load (%)', (CASE WHEN RxRes.IsExpectedPort=1 THEN (RxRes.FrameCount / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) ELSE 0 END) AS 'Rx Rate (fps)', ((Sb.MbpsLoad * 100.0) / Sb.PercentageLoad) AS 'Line Speed', 'True' AS 'Converged' FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle WHERE Sb.FixedFrameLength == 2048 AND Sb.PercentageLoad == 30.0 ORDER BY RxRes.DroppedFrameCount DESC, Sb.FpsLoad DESC LIMIT 1

Properties.Name: SqlQuery
Properties.Value: SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', CASE WHEN Sb.FpsLoad < 0 THEN 0.00 ELSE ROUND(Sb.FpsLoad-0.005,2) END AS 'Frames per Second', Sb.PercentageLoad AS 'Load %', Sb.MbpsLoad AS 'Load (Mbps)', ((((RxRes.L1BitCount / 1000000.0) / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) / ((Sb.MbpsLoad * 100.0) / Sb.PercentageLoad)) * 100.0) AS 'Rx Load (%)', (RxRes.FrameCount / ((RxRes.LastArrivalTime - RxRes.FirstArrivalTime) / 1000000.0)) AS 'Rx Rate (fps)', RxRes.SigFrameCount AS 'Rx Frame Count', RxRes.DroppedFrameCount AS 'Dropped Frame Count', RxRes.ReorderedFrameCount AS 'Reordered Frame Count', RxRes.DuplicateFrameCount AS 'Duplicate Frame Count', (SELECT Port.Location FROM Port WHERE Port.Handle = TxRes.ParentHnd) AS 'Tx Port', (SELECT Port.Location FROM Port WHERE Port.Handle = RxRes.ParentHnd) AS 'Rx Port', (CASE WHEN RxRes.IsExpectedPort=1 THEN 'True' ELSE 'False' END) AS 'Is Expected' From RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle WHERE Sb.FixedFrameLength == 2048 AND Sb.PercentageLoad == 30.0

report.display_name: RFC 2544 Throughput Check Against Threshold Percent of Theoretical Max Frame Rate

sql_statement.static: SELECT Res.FrameSize AS 'Frame Size', Res.FPS AS 'Throughput (Frames Per Second)',
CASE WHEN Res.MaxRate < 0 THEN 0.00 ELSE ROUND(Res.MaxRate-0.005,2) END
AS 'Theoretical Max Throughput (Frames Per Second)',
Res.DroppedCount AS 'Dropped Frame Count', Res.LineSpeed AS 'Port Line Speed (mbps)',
Conf.MaxTrafficRate AS 'Max Traffic Rate (Percent of Line Rate)',
CASE WHEN Res.MaxRate <= 0 THEN 0.00 ELSE ROUND((RES.MaxRate/100.0 * Conf.MaxTrafficRate - 0.005), 2) END
AS 'Throughput Threshold (Frames Per Second)',
ROUND((Res.MaxRate * Conf.MaxTrafficRate/100.0 *
/100.0)-0.005, 2) AS Threshold
FROM MethRfc2544ThroughputFrameRate AS Res, MethRfc2544ThroughputBinarySearchConfig AS Conf
WHERE (Threshold) > Res.FPS OR Res.DroppedCount > 0
